By Chibuike Nwabuko Abuja (Sundiata Post) –  Senate President,  Bukola Saraki’s #GrowNigeria Movement has arrived Owerri, the Imo State capital as part of his nation-wide consultations with PDP stakeholders and supporters ahead of the forthcoming primaries.  Recall that Saraki has embarked on awareness and consultation tour shortly after announcing his intention to contest for president under the platform of the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP).  Sundiata Post gathered that the Semane President will later today speak with PDP delegates and party executives about his vision to #GrowNigeria by creating more jobs and opportunities for all.  According to him, “Working together, we know that we can move our nation #Forward.          